# 💬 Concurrent Chat Server

A multithreaded chat server built in Java, allowing multiple clients to connect and communicate in real time.

> ⚠️ This project is currently a work in progress. Further enhancements and features are being implemented.

## 🧠 Key Concepts
- Java Socket Programming
- Multithreading
- Server/Client architecture
- Real-time message broadcasting

## 🚧 In Progress
- Improved user interface for clients
- User authentication system (planned)
- Private messaging (planned)
- Message history logging (planned)

## 🛠️ Technologies Used
- Java
- Java Sockets
- Threads

## 🎯 Objective
To practice Java networking and multithreading concepts by simulating a real-time, multi-user communication platform.

